summary: MOMO - Momo, the adorable Shiba Inu who’s always been by Kabosu’s side, is finally stepping into the spotlight! While Kabosu gained fame as the face of Doge, Momo quietly brought joy to those who knew her. Now, with Momo, we’re celebrating this lovable companion who symbolizes loyalty and friendship. It’s more than just a coin; it’s a community-driven tribute to a bond that has warmed hearts around the world.
